Package: spectator
Title: Interface to the Spectator Earth API
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Zivan",
           family = "Karaman",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "zivan.karaman@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8933-4589"))
Description: Provides interface to Spectator Earth API, mainly for 
    obtaining the acquisition plans and satellite overpasses for Sentinel-2, 
    Landsat-8 and Sentinel-1 satellites. Current position and trajectory can
    also be obtained for a much larger set of satellites.
